ass="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْفَوْزُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the success</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَظِيمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the great.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>9<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 64-10" id="10" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieved</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَّبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and denied</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[in] Our Verses,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْحَـٰبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are the) companions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Fire,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">abiding forever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">therein.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبِئْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And wretched is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَصِيرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the destination.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>10<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 64-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصَابَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">strikes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّصِيبَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disaster</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِإِذْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by (the) permission</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُؤْمِنۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَهْدِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He guides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَلْبَهُۥ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his heart.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱ